Package org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata

Class FabricEventParameterInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.EventParameterInfo
      • org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata.FabricEventParameterInfo
  • public class FabricEventParameterInfo
extends EventParameterInfo
    Holds additional information about a parameter of a smart contract event method.

    It is recommended to use FabricContractInfoBuilder to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
